Hi Martina, 

We are currently making some extensive changes to the website to enable better editing and functionality. It's a 4 week project, which we have commenced earlier this week. If ok with you, can I please hold on this task and implement it as part of the larger project?

@heath maybe I can do it but I need some login name and password. let me know.

Thanks,
Manuel M

Good morning Heath

I hope you and your family are keeping well and safe.

Could you please add the Flinders Uni and Ingham Institute of Applied Medical Research logos to the Research Affiliation section of our website footer. Both of these logos are already in our images library in our website.

Could you please hyperlink them to their home pages.

Also could you please hyperlink the existing 2 logos in the Research Affiliation section: Macquarie Uni & Sydney Uni.

As you can see there isn't a lot of real estate so am wondering whether the empty space between our contact details and "Subscribe to our newsletter" could be utilised for either the Research Affiliation section or could the following:

Proudly owned by Royal Rehab

Proudly operated by Royal Rehab

be moved up into this void?

Could you also please hyperlink the MetroRehab Hospital and Sargood on Collaroy logos to their home pages.

Thank you very much Heath for working your web magic again 😊

Kind regards
